										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Although we regularly focus on the ad copy you can use in Google Ads and the many strategies behind them, another area that can have a big impact on your performance are the ad assets (formerly extensions) that can accompany your ads.</p>
<p>In this article, we‚Äôre going to run through each of the types of assets you have available in Google Ads, talk about how they can be applied to your account, and give some examples for how you might want to take advantage of them.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
